## Installation and Build

### Downloading

To get the @PROJECT_NAME@, run the following command in your terminal:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/IHateGameDev/@PROJECT_NAME@.git
cd @PROJECT_NAME@

# Get APIMacros dependencies if they are not installed:
wget https://raw.github.com/IHateGameDev/APIMacros/APIMacros/*deps*

# Or clone and install it:
git clone https://github.com/IHateGameDev/APIMacros.git
cd APIMacros
cmake ./ -G Ninja && sudo ninja install
```

### Building

```bash
mkdir build && cd build
cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Releas -DLAUNCH_TESTS=ON .. -G Ninja
ninja

ninja install
```

